description:
Powerful Voyage Estimation Calculator

Netpas Estimator is an unique and practical calculator for tramper business sector.
It is a perfect tool for most of the major types of tramper business such as Voyage, Cargo Relet and Time Charter.
Each type of business can be easily compared so that you can figure out the best type of business.
With the same vessel, you can evaluate and compare Voyage Charter and Time Charter business.
With the same cargo, you can evaluate and compare Voyage and Cargo Relet business.
Netpas Estimator provides useful calculations and simulations to help your estimation simple and fast.
It will support your sales plan intensively for profitable business.
